quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  86,1,"Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay samada iyo Xiddigga guura."
  86,2,"Maxaa ku ogeysiiyey waxa uu xiddiga guura) yahay?"
  86,3,"Waa xiddiggaa iftiinka badan."
  86,4,"Ma jirto naf aanu kor joogin ilaaliye (malag)."
  86,5,"Ee ha fiiriyo qofka waxa laga abuuray."
  86,6,"Waxaa laga abuuray biyo horay u soo booda."
  86,7,"Oo ka yimaada dhabarka iyo feeraha dhexdood,"
  86,8,"Hubaal (Alle) wuu Karaa inuu u soo celiyo nolosha (dhimasho kaddib)."
  86,9,"Maalinta waxyaalaha qarsoon iyo siraha la soo bandhigi (xaqiiqdooda)."
  86,10,"Ma leh (gaalku Maalintaas) xoog ama wax u soo gargaara midna."
  86,11,"Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay cirka leh roobka soo noqnoqda."
  86,12,"Iyo dhulka dil-dillaaca badan (ee soo saara dhirta iyo daaqa),"
  86,13,"Kani (Qur'aanku) waa hadal dhab ah oo cad oo kala saara (xaqa iyo baadilka)."
  86,14,"Oo ma aha dhayal (dheel)."
  86,15,"(Gaaladu) wax bay dhagri oo qorsheyn."
  86,16,"Aniguna (sidoo kale) Waxaan qorsheyn qorshe."
  86,17,"Ee u sug gaalada: Daa wax yar."
